contest.title: Contest

need to extract.part1: The contest is not ready to start! You need to extract it.
need to extract.part2: This action will not start the contest, it will prepare the server. It's suggested to extract the contest as soon as possible to discover early eventual problems.

contest.not started: The contest has not started yet!
contest.extratime disclamer: You can set an extra time for all the contestants in case of problems that afflicts everyone. This action <1>is logged</1> and must be justified to the committee.
